mecrisp protocol details :

_ = bl   ^0A = ^NL   ^0D = ^CR
 

[Enter]           __ok.^0A

X[Enter]          _X_is_unknown.^0A

'_base[Enter]     __ok.^0A

'_X[Enter]        _X_not_found.^0A

:_Y[Enter]        __ok.^0A

.s[Enter]         __ok.^0A

;[Enter]          __ok.^0A

:_Y[Enter]        _Redefine_Y.^0A_ok.^0A

X[Enter]          _X_is_unknown.^0A

:_Y_.s_;[Enter]   _Redefine_Y.^0A_ok.^0A

drop[Enter]       __Stack_underflow^0A

cr[Enter]         _^0A_ok.^0A

:_test_.s_;[Enter]  __Ram_full^0A


